    * {{{https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-1203}[BATCH-1247]}} - Clean up multilineOrderJob sample

    * {{{https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-1203}[BATCH-1248]}} - Remove default from "merge" attribute in XSD

    * {{{https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-1203}[BATCH-1250]}} - <job/> should disallow <decision/>, <split/>, and <step/> if abstract=true

    * {{{https://jira.spring.io/browse/BATCH-1203}[BATCH-1251]}} - Use standard JPQL in JPA sample


